about.description: Mutex package for the ROS infrastructure on conda.
about.summary: Mutex package for the ROS infrastructure on conda.

name: ros-conda-mutex
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set ros_version = 'melodic' %}

package:
  name: ros-conda-mutex
  version: 1.0

build:
  number: 0
  # need to put this in conda_build_config.yml when more versions of ROS land.
  string: {{ ros_version }}
  noarch: generic
  run_exports:
    - ros-conda-mutex * {{ ros_version }}

requirements:
  build:
    # a couple of fake dep to make tests go through
    - make

test:
  commands:
    - exit 0

about:
  home: https://www.ros.org/
  description: |
    Mutex package for the ROS infrastructure on conda.
  summary: Mutex package for the ROS infrastructure on conda.
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE.txt

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - wolfv
    - lesteve
    - SylvainCorlay
